{"tid":1453863,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(請傳承精神) 救人為主，打狗為次","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:16:45.000Z","uid":38705,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c8484dcd14c6f2d647721410279bbd0901a508","tid":1453863,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:34:18.000Z","msg":"大家尋晚都睇過有段義士飛身救人片<br />\n當中需要嘅勇氣係非常之大<br />\n我唔係叫大家每個人都要即刻學佢（至少我都唔得）<br />\n心理同身理始終係需要時間去接受<br />\n但你忍心淨係自己走到<br />\n之後望住你身後嘅義士被狗捉到打頭開槍打甩牙咩？<br />\n我希望大家要抱返著起初一個都不能少嘅精神<br />\n走就一齊走，一個拉一個，唔好個個一轉身就跑<br />\n手足永遠都係我地最寶貴嘅力量"},{"pid":"a2532284d03ef0f9f4b154c7ecf61acfe9796bdb","tid":1453863,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:35:57.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"7aa1186bcd86dc3ba24d19705a4dd63f89dbfa80","tid":1453863,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:37:29.000Z","msg":"727"},{"pid":"d66c48ff09a0fc4e1ec4877c2e18ed0008198f85","tid":1453863,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"612"},{"pid":"0fed76960ecb2d2f1e412db98da5be81fed11d1b","tid":1453863,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:46:02.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"b1a69df9f0d7e5bc915f9f90ff9288bae3abd165","tid":1453863,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"727"},{"pid":"9c1b3cf0984d668ed697a2529b779500c879b126","tid":1453863,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:20:32.000Z","msg":"612"},{"pid":"9522cc3138cd4a157ba45d69a9fdb3ab2f188ed8","tid":1453863,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:29:50.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"bed5691f3db5dbcb711b4fa2794a1a3bef43e915","tid":1453863,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:10:01.000Z","msg":"We do not Forget.<br />\nWe do not Forgive.<br /